https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=17150	19440
Engadget从惠普搞到了平板电脑HP Slate的<a href="http://www.engadget.com/2010/04/05/hp-slate-to-cost-549-have-1-6ghz-atom-z530-5-hour-battery/">内部演示图片</a>。<i>
